snippet: Mr. Gusmão, who was the young country’s first president, submitted his resignation Friday as part of a reshuffling expected to bring more opposition figures into power.
abstract: East Timor's Prime Min Xanana Gusmao resigns amid political restructuring aimed at smoothing country's fractious politics.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Gusmão, who was the young country’s first president, submitted his resignation Friday as part of a reshuffling expected to bring more opposition figures into power.

headline.main: East Timor’s Prime Minister, Xanana Gusmão, Resigns
headline.print_headline: East Timor: Prime Minister Steps Down
